00:04:10.040 --> 00:04:12.480
'Bagaimana caranya aku bisa membakar menantu perempuanku?'

00:04:13.600 --> 00:04:15.400
'Tuan Jindal, di mana Anda?'

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:18.200
'Tolong segera ke Little Guddan.'

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:58.280
